So I enabled a few things in there,

40:16.680 --> 40:19.240
but upon rebooting, I learned a lot of things.

40:19.240 --> 40:22.960
So I rebooted into the installed system,

40:22.960 --> 40:25.080
which was fast and great.

40:25.080 --> 40:28.640
