48:50.980 --> 48:53.380
why would you spend three to six months

48:53.380 --> 48:55.900
creating an ad deal with some, you know.

48:55.900 --> 48:58.100
Smalls and twos and, right.

48:58.100 --> 48:59.380
This is a dramatic problem.

